article_title: Chinese Car Firm Qoros Makes Impact in Crash Test
article_text:
Upstart Chinese car maker Qoros Auto Co. completed a crucial step in its strategy to crack the premium segment of its home market Wednesday when it secured the highest score in a prominent European crash test.

Qoros, a joint venture between China's Chery Automobile Co. and investment group Israel Corp., received a five-star score from Euro NCAP for its Qoros Sedan 3. The result is crucial for it to develop an image of quality and...
